snippet.title: Reign of Guilds - pre-Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
Today we share gameplay video based on the pre-Alpha build, which is available for ROG Club members.

To mark this day we would like to announce "Pre-Alpha Sale": 15% discount & bonuses for pre-order.
https://reignofguilds.com/en/preorder/

ROGgoms up!
